task.summary: Semi-working affine gap algorithm added. pam250 table is wrong (maybe not?)
smith-waterman local alignment has been implemented with linear and affine gaps. needleman-wunsch algorithm has been improved. better program structure
static protein shuffling method has been added
static tree construction method has been added
progressive multiple sequence alignment has been implemented (Fitch Margoliash algorithm with distance calculation of Feng and Doolittle progressive alignment algorithm)
cluster stores protein instead of its number. Better look of evolutionary tree
cluster storage extended for group-to-group align. now resulting cluster contains 2 cluster or 2 proteins or cluster + protein.
final cluster list with one root node changed by rootCluster
MSA implemented (Gotoh algorithm A). May contain mistakes
